=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持黃色經濟圈，支持屬於香港嘅經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一起幫我親戚手減低工作量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思阻左大家小小時間睇我篇1999，雖然我知好多概念係唔同嘅po都見過，但係見到好多聯署唔夠人簽，更多黃店告急，只係希望大家唔好忘記。所以我都想大家幫我頂下，比更多人見到，多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/data/c15c9575f0213fe5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2Fdata%2Fc15c9575f0213fe5&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e610wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=46814403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/data/c15c9575f0213fe5</a><br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_499213_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_499213_0&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e610wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=2d037b2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_499213_0&h=9d88e327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_499213_0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"因為有間 燒賣皇后係黃 d人撈亂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"原來係咁，真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527af697fa9fdd0a2b8652d1c3675870a3f1fbea","tid":2020401,"uid":134908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"狗都唔食"},{"pid":"1f57b4de3990cd3ce6632fb0154b69309b1ef090","tid":2020401,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"4f025d2e65a68882bd6954fe6570fbc88dd4ab1d","tid":2020401,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"屌P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"947f6e544d8644b8ef1b33e8dea67fccc5f72d81","tid":2020401,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T01:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23319709bd8ff529ed3dc686ec65fa63f9d13503","tid":2020401,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}